node.text: “I was never a big heavy weight, when I was in my prime I never weighed over 217 - 219, but me and my trainer Cus D’Amato we always put a great deal of emphasis on our speed and combinations. He always told me "speed kills, speed is what kills, the speed kills" - Mike Tyson
